"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.14.1.8\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.14.1.8</span> Other features of the Temple treated elsewhere in this chapter</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">Beams - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.5.3 Crossbeam, rafter&lt;REALIA:3.1.5.3&gt;</a></h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>Chains - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.21.4 Chain&lt;REALIA:3.21.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Courtyards - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.20 Courtyard, court&lt;REALIA:3.20&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Doors - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2 Door, doorway&lt;REALIA:3.1.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Doorposts - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.4 Doorpost&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Fortress - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.2 Fortress, stronghold, castle, citadel, fort&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Foundation - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.1 Foundation&lt;REALIA:3.1.1&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Gates - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.5 City gate&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Gateways - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.3 Gate or gateway to house or building complex&lt;REALIA:3.1.3&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Guardrooms - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.5.2 Guardroom&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.5.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Hinges - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.3 Hinge&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.3&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Holy Place - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.15.2.1 Holy Place&lt;REALIA:3.15.2.1&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Lintels - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.5 Lintel&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Most Holy Place - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.15.2.2 Holy of Holies, Most Holy Place&lt;REALIA:3.15.2.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Networks on capitals - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.5 Column, pillar, capital&lt;REALIA:3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Pillars - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.5 Column, pillar, capital&lt;REALIA:3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Roof - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.5 Roof, housetop&lt;REALIA:3.1.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Stairs, steps - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.7 Stairs, steps&lt;REALIA:3.1.7&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Stories - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.6.3 Wall&lt;REALIA:3.1.6.3&gt;</a> and <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.6.4 Upper room, roof chamber&lt;REALIA:3.1.6.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Thresholds - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.6 Threshold, doorsill&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.6&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Windows - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.4 Window&lt;REALIA:3.1.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>Walls - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.6 Boundary wall, fence&lt;REALIA:3.6&gt;</a></p>\n</div>\n</